<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Review Application</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="page">
      <header class="topbar">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow">Application #<%= app.id %></p>
          <h1><%= portal === "manager" ? app.answers.ign : "Anonymous Applicant" %></h1>
        </div>
        <div class="topbar-actions">
          <a href="/dashboard?search=<%= encodeURIComponent(searchQuery || "") %>" class="button button-ghost">Back to Queue</a>
        </div>
      </header>

      <% if (notice) { %>
      <section class="notice success"><%= notice %></section>
      <% } %>
      <% if (error) { %>
      <section class="notice error"><%= error %></section>
      <% } %>

      <section class="panel">
        <article>
          <h2>Application Answers</h2>

          <% if (portal === "manager") { %>
          <h3>Page 1</h3>
          <p><strong>IGN:</strong> <%= app.answers.ign %></p>
          <p><strong>Discord User:</strong> <%= app.answers.discordUser %></p>
          <p><strong>Discord UID:</strong> <%= app.answers.discordUid %></p>
          <p><strong>Age:</strong> <%= app.answers.age %></p>
          <p><strong>Timezone:</strong> <%= app.answers.timezone %></p>

          <h3>Page 2</h3>
          <p><strong>Preferred Side:</strong> <%= app.answers.preferredSide %></p>
          <p><strong>Working Microphone:</strong> <%= app.answers.hasMicrophone %></p>
          <p><strong>Streaming/Recording:</strong> <%= app.answers.streamingInfo %></p>
          <% } %>

          <h3>Page 3</h3>
          <p><strong>Without telling us who you are, tell us a little bit about yourself:</strong></p>
          <p><%= app.answers.aboutYourself %></p>
          <p><strong>What are your goals for this event?</strong></p>
          <p><%= app.answers.eventGoals %></p>
          <p><strong>Describe your past experience with Minecraft events, roleplay events, and story-telling. Please be specific with your answers.</strong></p>
          <p><%= app.answers.pastEventExperience %></p>
          <p><strong>Describe a character you may create for this event. Please be specific with your answers.</strong></p>
          <p><%= app.answers.characterDescription %></p>
          <p><strong>Tell us about a time that something went wrong for you - did you fail? How did you fail? What did you do when you failed?</strong></p>
          <p><%= app.answers.failureStory %></p>

          <h3>Page 4</h3>
          <p><strong>Three pirates corner you, demanding you hand over your gear and your valuables. You don't have much on you, but you have a few diamonds that you found in a chest nearby. What do you do?</strong></p>
          <p><%= app.answers.scenarioPiratesCornerYou %></p>
          <p><strong>You come across a group of sailors that have been stranded on an island with very little food. They are hungry, and you and your team has an abundance of bread and cooked steak. What do you do?</strong></p>
          <p><%= app.answers.scenarioStrandedSailors %></p>
        </article>
      </section>

    </main>
  </body>
</html>
